welcome_message_body: "Welcome to charming Elfers, where small town charm meets natural beauty. We invite you to explore our quaint streets, renowned for their local shops and restaurants, and soak up the relaxing atmosphere that our city is known for. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Executive Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Executive Airport caters to executive and luxury flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily international flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for up to 45 minutes per session.

terminals.name: Airside Terminal

terminals.name: Main Terminal
